D.aZa=new B.n("The control can be used with a custom value class. With this feature, AutoSuggestBox can be used as a replacement of a ComboBox.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
D.aZc=new B.n("A NumberFormBox",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
D.aZj=new B.n("The PasswordBox is almost identical to the TextBox. But the character is obfuscated by default and a button in the suffix allow the user to show briefly the password in plain text.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
D.aZn=new B.n("By default, a combo box lets the user select from a pre-defined list of options. However, there are cases where the list contains only a subset of valid values, and the user should be able to enter other values that aren't listed. To support this, you can make the combo box editable.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
